Three new species of the leafhopper genus Tambocerus Zhang & Webb (Hemiptera, Cicadellidae) from southern ChinaAbstract Three new species, Tambocerus dentatus, T. longicaudatus and T. robustispinus spp. n. from southern China, are described and illustrated. A checklist and distribution to the Tambocerus species from China is provided together with a key for their separation.